00:15:54.010 --> 00:15:57.810
puzzles were lifted
from a puzzle book

00:15:57.810 --> 00:16:00.030
published by MENSA.

00:16:00.030 --> 00:16:02.790
Have any of you heard
of MENSA?

00:16:02.790 --> 00:16:07.880
MENSA is an association of
self-declared geniuses.

00:16:07.880 --> 00:16:10.120
So this was a puzzle
book for geniuses.

00:16:10.120 --> 00:16:14.200
And you all did horribly well
