00:45:15.940 --> 00:45:22.940
has the same thing hanging
about, two translations that

00:45:22.940 --> 00:45:27.400
are exactly 90 degrees apart.

00:45:27.400 --> 00:45:32.030
So what we're doing is taking
a four-fold axis and drop it

00:45:32.030 --> 00:45:36.030
in at the corner lattice point
and then step back before all

00:45:36.030 --> 00:45:37.872
hell breaks looks.

00:45:37.872 --> 00:45:40.510
Now, first thing we're gonna
